---
const weeks = Array.from({ length: 12 }, (_, index) => index + 1);
---

<div class="process-artifact">
  <div class="process-artifact__meta">
    <span class="label">Capacidad por semana</span>
    <span class="status-chip"><span class="status-dot"></span> demo cada viernes</span>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline" aria-hidden="true" data-animate="scale-x" data-stagger="90">
    <span class="timeline__corner"></span>
    {weeks.map((week) => <span class="timeline__week">S{week}</span>)}

    <span class="timeline__label">TRABAJO</span>
    <span class="timeline__phase timeline__phase--diagnosis">DIAGNÓSTICO</span>
    <span class="timeline__phase timeline__phase--build">CONSTRUCCIÓN — ENTREGA</span>

    <span class="timeline__label">FELIPE</span>
    <span class="timeline__bar timeline__bar--owner"><i class="timeline__bar-fill" data-animate-item data-motion-index="0"></i></span>

    <span class="timeline__label">NÚCLEO</span>
    <span class="timeline__bar timeline__bar--core"><i class="timeline__bar-fill" data-animate-item data-motion-index="1"></i></span>

    <span class="timeline__label">RED FLEX.</span>
    <span class="timeline__bar timeline__bar--flex">
      <i class="timeline__bar-fill" data-animate-item data-motion-index="2"></i>
      <span class="timeline__bar-copy">SOLO SI SE EXIGE</span>
    </span>

    <span class="timeline__label timeline__label--production">DEMO</span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--1"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--2"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--3"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--4"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--5"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--6"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--7"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--8"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--9"></span>
    <span class="timeline__demo timeline__demo--10"></span>
  </div>

  <div class="mobile-lanes" aria-hidden="true" data-animate="scale-x" data-stagger="90">
    <span class="mobile-lanes__corner">ROL / RITMO</span><span>SEM. 1–2</span><span class="mobile-lanes__last">SEM. 3–12+</span>
    <span class="mobile-lanes__label">FELIPE</span><i class="mobile-lanes__bar mobile-lanes__bar--owner"><span class="mobile-lanes__fill" data-animate-item data-motion-index="0"></span></i><i class="mobile-lanes__bar mobile-lanes__bar--owner mobile-lanes__last"><span class="mobile-lanes__fill" data-animate-item data-motion-index="0"></span></i>
    <span class="mobile-lanes__label">NÚCLEO</span><i class="mobile-lanes__empty">—</i><i class="mobile-lanes__bar mobile-lanes__bar--core mobile-lanes__last"><span class="mobile-lanes__fill" data-animate-item data-motion-index="1"></span></i>
    <span class="mobile-lanes__label">RED FLEX.</span><i class="mobile-lanes__bar mobile-lanes__bar--flex mobile-lanes__last"><span class="mobile-lanes__fill" data-animate-item data-motion-index="2"></span><span class="mobile-lanes__bar-copy">SEGÚN ALCANCE</span></i>
    <span class="mobile-lanes__label mobile-lanes__label--demo">DEMO</span><i class="mobile-lanes__demo">PRIMERO</i><i class="mobile-lanes__demo mobile-lanes__last">VIERNES</i>
  </div>

  <dl class="mobile-timeline">
    <div>
      <dt>Semanas 1–2</dt>
      <dd><strong>Diagnóstico.</strong> Felipe participa; el primer demo aparece entre la semana 1 y 2.</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Semanas 3–12+</dt>
      <dd><strong>Construcción y entrega.</strong> Felipe sigue; entra el núcleo de ingeniería y se demuestra software cada viernes.</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Cuando se exige</dt>
      <dd><strong>Especialistas.</strong> La red flexible entra solo para una capacidad concreta.</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>

  <p class="process-artifact__summary sr-only">
    Felipe permanece durante todo el proyecto. El núcleo de ingeniería entra al construir; especialistas adicionales participan solo cuando son necesarios. Desde el primer demo, se muestra software cada viernes.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .process-artifact {
    padding: clamp(var(--space-5), 4vw, var(--space-7));
    border: var(--border) solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background-color: var(--paper-raised);
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(to right, color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 54%, transparent) var(--border), transparent var(--border)),
      linear-gradient(to bottom, color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 38%, transparent) var(--border), transparent var(--border));
    background-size: 3.5rem 3.5rem;
  }

  .process-artifact__meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .process-artifact__meta > .label {
    color: var(--graphite);
  }

  .timeline {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 7.5rem repeat(12, minmax(0, 1fr));
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2) var(--border);
  }

  .timeline__week,
  .timeline__label,
  .timeline__phase,
  .timeline__bar,
  .timeline__demo {
    font-family: var(--font-data);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .timeline__week {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: var(--text-tiny);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .timeline__demo::before,
  .mobile-lanes__demo::before {
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    display: inline-block;
    border-right: 0.3em solid transparent;
    border-bottom: 0.48em solid currentColor;
    border-left: 0.3em solid transparent;
    content: "";
  }

  .timeline__label {
    padding-right: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: var(--text-tiny);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .timeline__label--production {
    color: var(--production);
  }

  .timeline__phase {
    min-height: var(--space-6);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border: var(--border) solid currentColor;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--paper-raised);
    font-size: var(--text-tiny);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .timeline__phase--diagnosis {
    grid-column: 2 / 4;
    color: var(--manual);
  }

  .timeline__phase--build {
    grid-column: 4 / 14;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .timeline__bar {
    position: relative;
    min-height: var(--space-3);
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .timeline__bar-fill,
  .mobile-lanes__fill {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: block;
    transform-origin: left center;
  }

  .timeline__bar--owner {
    grid-column: 2 / 14;
  }

  .timeline__bar--owner .timeline__bar-fill,
  .mobile-lanes__bar--owner .mobile-lanes__fill {
    background: var(--ink);
  }

  .timeline__bar--core {
    grid-column: 4 / 14;
  }

  .timeline__bar--core .timeline__bar-fill,
  .mobile-lanes__bar--core .mobile-lanes__fill {
    background: var(--graphite);
  }

  .timeline__bar--flex {
    min-height: var(--space-5);
    grid-column: 7 / 11;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border: var(--border) dashed var(--line-strong);
    color: var(--graphite);
    font-size: var(--text-nano);
  }

  .timeline__bar--flex .timeline__bar-fill,
  .mobile-lanes__bar--flex .mobile-lanes__fill {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--graphite) 12%, transparent);
  }

  .timeline__bar-copy,
  .mobile-lanes__bar-copy {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline__demo {
    color: var(--production);
    font-size: var(--text-micro);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .timeline__demo--1 { grid-column: 4; }
  .timeline__demo--2 { grid-column: 5; }
  .timeline__demo--3 { grid-column: 6; }
  .timeline__demo--4 { grid-column: 7; }
  .timeline__demo--5 { grid-column: 8; }
  .timeline__demo--6 { grid-column: 9; }
  .timeline__demo--7 { grid-column: 10; }
  .timeline__demo--8 { grid-column: 11; }
  .timeline__demo--9 { grid-column: 12; }
  .timeline__demo--10 { grid-column: 13; }

  .mobile-lanes,
  .mobile-timeline {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 56.25rem) {
    .timeline {
      display: none;
    }

    .process-artifact__summary {
      display: none;
    }

    .mobile-lanes {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(5.25rem, 0.72fr) repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      align-items: center;
      border: var(--border) solid var(--line);
      font-family: var(--font-data);
      font-size: var(--text-nano);
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }

    .mobile-lanes > * {
      min-width: 0;
      min-height: var(--space-6);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: var(--space-2);
      border-right: var(--border) solid var(--line);
      border-bottom: var(--border) solid var(--line);
      font-style: normal;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .mobile-lanes__last {
      border-right: 0;
    }

    .mobile-lanes__corner,
    .mobile-lanes__label {
      justify-items: start;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .mobile-lanes__bar {
      position: relative;
      width: calc(100% - var(--space-3));
      min-height: var(--space-3);
      align-self: center;
      justify-self: center;
      padding: 0;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .mobile-lanes__bar--flex {
      min-height: var(--space-5);
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
      width: calc(100% - var(--space-3));
      border: var(--border) dashed var(--line-strong);
      color: var(--graphite);
    }

    .mobile-lanes__empty {
      color: var(--line-strong);
    }

    .mobile-lanes__label--demo,
    .mobile-lanes__demo {
      color: var(--production);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .mobile-timeline {
      display: grid;
      margin-top: var(--space-4);
      gap: 0;
    }

    .mobile-timeline div {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(7rem, 0.6fr) 1.4fr;
      gap: var(--space-5);
      padding-block: var(--space-4);
      border-top: var(--border) solid var(--line);
    }

    .mobile-timeline dt {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--font-data);
      font-size: var(--text-label);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .mobile-timeline dd {
      color: var(--graphite);
      font-size: var(--text-micro);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .mobile-timeline strong {
      color: var(--ink);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 37.4375rem) {
    .process-artifact__meta {
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .mobile-timeline div {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }
  }
</style>
